pullRequest.body:
Introduces the final whole-number separation axiom: [perfectly normal](https://topology.pi-base.org/properties/P000015) / [$T_6$](https://topology.pi-base.org/properties/P000067). Includes a proof that perfectly normal implies completely normal (resp. $T_6$ implies $T_5$). Future work: show all pseudometrizable spaces are perfectly normal (resp. all metrizable spaces are $T_6$).

---

- [x] depends on: #13176
- [x] depends on: #13694

---
